All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AppInitializer
Class used to Initialize entire Market application
Asset
This is root class for all assets available in the market
AssetBackedByCurrency
In general if something is Backed by some particular currency.
AssetFactory
Function for creating new Assets
AssetPlotController
Controller for plotting different Assets
AssetPriceRule
Interface defining what operations should any object responsible for regulating the Prices for Assets implement
BasicAssetPriceRule
Function that given some change in parameters with 50% chance changes the ratio
BiggestCompaniesFilter
Sorts companies based on their current price
Commodity
Class representing commodity In the world.
CompaniesFilter
Interface which allows for filtering companies based on some rule
Company
Class representing real company that issue shares and generates some profit etc.
CompanyObserver
 
CompanySubject
 
Constants
Class containing all constant used in simulation, so that we are not using some magic values.

Class representing Currency in our world.
Dealer
 
DynamicMarketIndex

ExchangeRatesProvider
 
HumanInvestor
Class representing investor that can buy on the investment fund
InvestmentFund
Class representing Investment Fund -> which can issue some units that can be bought by traders so we can also trade with this class members If we are human Investors
InvestmentFundUnit
Class representing Investment Fund Unit in our World
MainPanelController
Main controller of the entire application All methods with add prefix are self explanatory methods with Show are used to show/hide particular TableViews
Market
Market is a container for Assets that can be bought on it.
MarketDetailsController
Controller for showing additional informations about Market
MarketFactory
Function for creating markets
MarketIndex
Class representing Market Index in the real world
MarketWithIndices
If market is with indices we can additionally buy Indices on it.
ObjectCounter
Class that takes care of counting amounts of each type of object in the world
ObjectsAdder
Class bein able to add new objects to the world in that case it does it randomly.
PositiveTransactionSystem
 
RandomString
 
Searchable

Class for generating all kinds of random values.
Share
Class representing share in our world
StartupsCompaniesFilter

StrictTransactionSystem
 
TableFiller
Class used to fill TableViews with different kind of data
TableFilter
 
TooltipTableRow<T>
Extra class for menaging Tooltips and making them refreshable
Trader
Base class for all types of object that can perform some trading on a market.
TraderDetailsController
Controller for showing additional information about trader
TraderFactory
Function which we can use to create new Traders
TransactionSystem
Interface allowing for buying and selling stuff
World
World is basically a container of all markets, assets, traders and is also has an interface for adding new objects to it
WorldContainer
Container for all objects stored in the world
WorldThread
Thread responsible for simulating the "time" in the simulation.
